      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Issues:\nNot reliable\nSingle point of failure",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Issues:\nNot reliable\nSingle point of failure",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 218,
      "versionNonce": 273882729,
      "index": "aU",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "7sxTpTXfUTIGWD2mx8BJe",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 972.09765625,
      "y": 490.0546875,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 85.6639404296875,
      "height": 20,
      "seed": 1366113944,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "single Node",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "single Node",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 826,
      "versionNonce": 683874471,
      "index": "aV",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "rmr0WLIRofAXZ1YvPTs9i",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 891.2734375,
      "y": 716.015625,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 444.8477783203125,
      "height": 400,
      "seed": 2022417128,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "How to make it better? \n  ONLY REPLICA\n  - multiple replica of Counter node\n      PROS.              \n      * helps scale reads from our client\n      * no single point of failure\n\n    \n\n  REPLICAS + SNAPSHOTS\n    - All replica\n    - Periodically snapshot our memory\n    PROS\n     * allows us to scale out reads from our Client.\n     * quick recover from failure\n     * we'll load the most recent snapshot \n       and re-read from our stream until we \"catch up\".\n     * we're in a much more fault-tolerant state\n       \n     ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How to make it better? \n  ONLY REPLICA\n  - multiple replica of Counter node\n      PROS.              \n      * helps scale reads from our client\n      * no single point of failure\n\n    \n\n  REPLICAS + SNAPSHOTS\n    - All replica\n    - Periodically snapshot our memory\n    PROS\n     * allows us to scale out reads from our Client.\n     * quick recover from failure\n     * we'll load the most recent snapshot \n       and re-read from our stream until we \"catch up\".\n     * we're in a much more fault-tolerant state\n       \n     ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 484,
      "versionNonce": 185952585,
      "index": "aX",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "AXFubJTXG0fK9cJf2duYR",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1258.2734375,
      "y": 751.015625,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 370.0478515625,
      "height": 180,
      "seed": 728383384,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "CONS\n* increase load on View stream\n* multiply the hardware need \n* with replica only, in failure we have to \n  remove the failed instance and, new instance\n  \"catch-up\" can take longer, requires stream \n   retention.\n\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CONS\n* increase load on View stream\n* multiply the hardware need \n* with replica only, in failure we have to \n  remove the failed instance and, new instance\n  \"catch-up\" can take longer, requires stream \n   retention.\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 455,
      "versionNonce": 1783065543,
      "index": "aY",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "GfibrQ7lkvF5CI3DppMhN",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1356,
      "y": 957,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 408.0638427734375,
      "height": 200,
      "seed": 490184936,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "CONS/Challenges\n * we still need retention on stream\n   till catch-up but we can drop after that.\n * snapshotting increases system overhead as\n   they'll be multi-GB (dragging down throughput). \n * We'll need 1 second to recover for every second \n   that has passed since the last snapshot.\n * need mechanism to make sure \n   snapshots are internally consistent.\n ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CONS/Challenges\n * we still need retention on stream\n   till catch-up but we can drop after that.\n * snapshotting increases system overhead as\n   they'll be multi-GB (dragging down throughput). \n * We'll need 1 second to recover for every second \n   that has passed since the last snapshot.\n * need mechanism to make sure \n   snapshots are internally consistent.\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 287,
      "versionNonce": 1359697961,
      "index": "ac",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "UGcoBarinNVWpxtnXjUYO",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 924,
      "y": 1187,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 430.09576416015625,
      "height": 160,
      "seed": 1018162328,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "SCALE WRITE THROUGHPUT \n  Sharding/Partitioning (Elastic Partitioning)\n   * change number and size of partitions dynamically \n     (crucial for handling varying workloads)\n   * When we need to add more capacity, new shards \n     are spun up which read from different snapshots.\n   \n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "SCALE WRITE THROUGHPUT \n  Sharding/Partitioning (Elastic Partitioning)\n   * change number and size of partitions dynamically \n     (crucial for handling varying workloads)\n   * When we need to add more capacity, new shards \n     are spun up which read from different snapshots.\n   \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 350,
      "versionNonce": 437541607,
      "index": "ae",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "5p0ngPsfQFAaQOP76r38h",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1376.41796875,
      "y": 1195.34375,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 352.0957946777344,
      "height": 200,
      "seed": 751086488,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720053704996,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Challenges\n * Since our partitions are no longer fixed, \n  we need registry like \"Zookeeper\" so that \n  each shards knows its assignment and \n  the Top-K service knows which shards \n  to query.\n\n * Num of SHARDS becoming large requiring \n  a large, scatter-gather operation.\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Challenges\n * Since our partitions are no longer fixed, \n  we need registry like \"Zookeeper\" so that \n  each shards knows its assignment and \n  the Top-K service knows which shards \n  to query.\n\n * Num of SHARDS becoming large requiring \n  a large, scatter-gather operation.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
