      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "simple solution for all-time top K videos which we'll build on a gigantic single host,\n\nCounts: table of video IDs and counts. updated with count of every video. \nTop-k heap: heap of the top K videos which we can update with each increment. \n\nMajority of views will never touch this heap since they'll \nbe below the threshold.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "simple solution for all-time top K videos which we'll build on a gigantic single host,\n\nCounts: table of video IDs and counts. updated with count of every video. \nTop-k heap: heap of the top K videos which we can update with each increment. \n\nMajority of views will never touch this heap since they'll \nbe below the threshold.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
