      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1720760596083,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Handling URL Fetch Failure\n- SQS supports retries with configurable \n  exponential backoff.\n- After a certain number of failures, \n  the message is moved to a dead-letter queue (DLQ). \n  At this stage, the message is considered unprocessable \n   (say after 5 retries).",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Handling URL Fetch Failure\n- SQS supports retries with configurable \n  exponential backoff.\n- After a certain number of failures, \n  the message is moved to a dead-letter queue (DLQ). \n  At this stage, the message is considered unprocessable \n   (say after 5 retries).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
