    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 53,
      "versionNonce": 1601430586,
      "index": "b2J",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "Ri8Zyd8KB9ifB63R3L7Jy",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 345.21068602285334,
      "y": 6642.031346639206,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1266.839599609375,
      "height": 405,
      "seed": 2076682470,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1721972327880,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Functional Req: \n - Upload video and images from IoT devices.\n - Support MP4 video format\n - Smooth video streaming.\n - Ability to change video quality (Adaptive (bitrate) streaming).\n - Accessible only to authenticated and authorized users.\n - Handle large video files, potentially through asynchronous processing. \n - Support multiple video streaming protocols, starting with RTSP.\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Req: \n - Upload video and images from IoT devices.\n - Support MP4 video format\n - Smooth video streaming.\n - Ability to change video quality (Adaptive (bitrate) streaming).\n - Accessible only to authenticated and authorized users.\n - Handle large video files, potentially through asynchronous processing. \n - Support multiple video streaming protocols, starting with RTSP.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 15,
      "versionNonce": 516775974,
      "index": "b2K",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "XP_hdN5lyXsMhZTKb4vg4",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 347.3293232440733,
      "y": 7122.961995856137,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1117.043701171875,
      "height": 360,
      "seed": 371567418,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1721972400411,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Non-Functional Req: \n- 100 million DAU.\n- Low latency for upload and retrieval.\n- Availability > Consistency\n- Resumable Upload\n- Implement encryption for data in transit (TLS).\n- Authentication and authorization mechanisms (OAuth2, JWT).\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-Functional Req: \n- 100 million DAU.\n- Low latency for upload and retrieval.\n- Availability > Consistency\n- Resumable Upload\n- Implement encryption for data in transit (TLS).\n- Authentication and authorization mechanisms (OAuth2, JWT).\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 504,
      "versionNonce": 1127658823,
      "index": "b2M",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "tuoAsaPMseaIrGyLQ2vsj",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 322.94844334675304,
      "y": 8401.624098244007,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 893.0877647399902,
      "height": 1035,
      "seed": 2035827514,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1722183860380,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "API Endpoints (This may not be applicable \nfor IoT media streaming): \n 1. Video Upload\n   POST /api/media/video\n   Fields: device_id, stream_url, format\n\n2. Image Upload \n   POST /media/image\n   Fields: \n   device_id, \n   image_data: Binary (the image file)\n   format: String (default to JPEG/PNG)\n\n3. Media Retrieval\n   GET /media/{device_id}\n   Response:\n   media_list: (list of media files with metadata)\n\n4. Video Stream Start\n   POST /api/media/start_stream\n   Request Fields:\n     device_id, stream_url:\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API Endpoints (This may not be applicable \nfor IoT media streaming): \n 1. Video Upload\n   POST /api/media/video\n   Fields: device_id, stream_url, format\n\n2. Image Upload \n   POST /media/image\n   Fields: \n   device_id, \n   image_data: Binary (the image file)\n   format: String (default to JPEG/PNG)\n\n3. Media Retrieval\n   GET /media/{device_id}\n   Response:\n   media_list: (list of media files with metadata)\n\n4. Video Stream Start\n   POST /api/media/start_stream\n   Request Fields:\n     device_id, stream_url:\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 68,
      "versionNonce": 314805801,
      "index": "b2N",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "FKk0oFlOyzknhoaS4uWRO",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 330.38022547431376,
      "y": 7540.333528436464,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1493.315845489502,
      "height": 855,
      "seed": 1087900390,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1722125218684,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Back-of-the-Envelope Calculation (100M DAU):\n- Assuming an average video stream of 2Mbps and an average \n  image size of 1MB, the total daily data ingestion would be:\n\n  * Video: 100M users * 2Mbps * 60 secs * 60 mins * 24 hrs \n          = 172.8 PB (around 200 PB)\n  * Images: 100M users * 1MB * 10 images per day = 1 PB\n\n  Total daily data ingestion: 173.8 PB  (around 200 PB)\n\n- Considering a 3x replication factor for data redundancy and availability, \n  the total storage requirement would be approximately 521.4 PB (around 600 PB).\n\n- Assuming an average video watch time of 10 minutes per day, the total daily \n  video streaming bandwidth would be:\n  100M users * 2Mbps * 10 minutes = 20 PB\n\nQPS ?\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back-of-the-Envelope Calculation (100M DAU):\n- Assuming an average video stream of 2Mbps and an average \n  image size of 1MB, the total daily data ingestion would be:\n\n  * Video: 100M users * 2Mbps * 60 secs * 60 mins * 24 hrs \n          = 172.8 PB (around 200 PB)\n  * Images: 100M users * 1MB * 10 images per day = 1 PB\n\n  Total daily data ingestion: 173.8 PB  (around 200 PB)\n\n- Considering a 3x replication factor for data redundancy and availability, \n  the total storage requirement would be approximately 521.4 PB (around 600 PB).\n\n- Assuming an average video watch time of 10 minutes per day, the total daily \n  video streaming bandwidth would be:\n  100M users * 2Mbps * 10 minutes = 20 PB\n\nQPS ?\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 55,
      "versionNonce": 801142118,
      "index": "b2Q",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "RzcSN2yQRaqaWFKuo9CXm",
