      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "We can use Amazon SQS here. SQS offers a feature where it deletes the message onces consumed by the consumer. This will help save storage space.\nAbove diagram can be further updated to have a common SQS Queue (partioned) instead of dedicated queue for each stage and respective worker will \nread from that queue/topic. ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We can use Amazon SQS here. SQS offers a feature where it deletes the message onces consumed by the consumer. This will help save storage space.\nAbove diagram can be further updated to have a common SQS Queue (partioned) instead of dedicated queue for each stage and respective worker will \nread from that queue/topic. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
