      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Reads add/update data from \nPostgres transaction logs (Write Ahead Logs)\nand publish to respective topics",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Reads add/update data from \nPostgres transaction logs (Write Ahead Logs)\nand publish to respective topics",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 484,
      "versionNonce": 704515905,
      "index": "b8v",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "d-oZRD8m0nLZ44jheG_uP",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 2921.3235868920565,
      "y": 15162.121014397262,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1089.3596076965332,
      "height": 405,
      "seed": 1541570785,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1723148098737,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "- Follows Medallion Architecture Pattern\n- Delta table for each data or DB table\n- Views that needs to be exposed to other consumers\n\n* Future Change: \n  - Move CDC in Databricks where data will be published\n    to topic from Delta table when it's added (even-driven)\n  - Delta table can be configured to read data directly from \n    Attribution topic, i.e., no need to middle layer.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Follows Medallion Architecture Pattern\n- Delta table for each data or DB table\n- Views that needs to be exposed to other consumers\n\n* Future Change: \n  - Move CDC in Databricks where data will be published\n    to topic from Delta table when it's added (even-driven)\n  - Delta table can be configured to read data directly from \n    Attribution topic, i.e., no need to middle layer.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
