      "fontSize": 47.860156155967,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "* User\n  POST /users/register: Register a new user (customer, restaurant, delivery partner).\n  POST /users/login: Log in a user.\n  GET /users/profile: Get user profile data.\n  PUT /users/profile: Update user profile data.\n\n* Restaurant\n  GET /restaurants: List restaurants based on location and filters.\n  GET /restaurants/{id}/menu: Get the menu for a specific restaurant.\n  POST /restaurants/{id}/menu: Update restaurant menu.\n\n* Order\n  POST /orders: Place an order.\n  GET /orders/{id}: Get order status.\n  PUT /orders/{id}/cancel: Cancel an order.\n\n* Delivery\n  GET /delivery/partners: Get available delivery partners.\n  PUT /delivery/{id}/status: Update delivery status (picked up, in transit, delivered).\n\n* Payment\n  POST /payments: Process payment for an order.\n\n* Rating & Reviews\n  POST /reviews: Submit a review for a restaurant or delivery partner.\n  GET /reviews/{id}: Fetch reviews for a specific entity.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "* User\n  POST /users/register: Register a new user (customer, restaurant, delivery partner).\n  POST /users/login: Log in a user.\n  GET /users/profile: Get user profile data.\n  PUT /users/profile: Update user profile data.\n\n* Restaurant\n  GET /restaurants: List restaurants based on location and filters.\n  GET /restaurants/{id}/menu: Get the menu for a specific restaurant.\n  POST /restaurants/{id}/menu: Update restaurant menu.\n\n* Order\n  POST /orders: Place an order.\n  GET /orders/{id}: Get order status.\n  PUT /orders/{id}/cancel: Cancel an order.\n\n* Delivery\n  GET /delivery/partners: Get available delivery partners.\n  PUT /delivery/{id}/status: Update delivery status (picked up, in transit, delivered).\n\n* Payment\n  POST /payments: Process payment for an order.\n\n* Rating & Reviews\n  POST /reviews: Submit a review for a restaurant or delivery partner.\n  GET /reviews/{id}: Fetch reviews for a specific entity.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
