      "updated": 1727672205627,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 52.653317758934485,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Microservices Responsibilities: \n- User Service: \n    Handles user information (login, profile, etc.).\n- Restaurant Service: \n    Fetches restaurant menus, availability, and reviews.\n- Order Service: \n   Manages the lifecycle of orders (placing, updating, \n   canceling).\n- Delivery Service: \n   Manages delivery partner assignments, real-time status \n   updates, and order tracking.\n    1. Queries Real-Time Tracking DB for nearby delivery partner.\n    2. Matches available partner based on location and status.\n    3. Updates assignment in SQL Orders DB.\n    4. Sends push notification via Notification Service to driver.\n    5. Tracks real-time updates from driver using Real-Time DB.\n\n- Payment Service: \n    Handles transactions securely, working with external \n    payment gateways (e.g., Stripe, PayPal).\n- Notification Service: \n   Sends real-time notifications (e.g., order confirmation, \n   delivery status updates).",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Microservices Responsibilities: \n- User Service: \n    Handles user information (login, profile, etc.).\n- Restaurant Service: \n    Fetches restaurant menus, availability, and reviews.\n- Order Service: \n   Manages the lifecycle of orders (placing, updating, \n   canceling).\n- Delivery Service: \n   Manages delivery partner assignments, real-time status \n   updates, and order tracking.\n    1. Queries Real-Time Tracking DB for nearby delivery partner.\n    2. Matches available partner based on location and status.\n    3. Updates assignment in SQL Orders DB.\n    4. Sends push notification via Notification Service to driver.\n    5. Tracks real-time updates from driver using Real-Time DB.\n\n- Payment Service: \n    Handles transactions securely, working with external \n    payment gateways (e.g., Stripe, PayPal).\n- Notification Service: \n   Sends real-time notifications (e.g., order confirmation, \n   delivery status updates).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
