      "updated": 1727673253452,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 44.204005861528586,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Real Time Tracking DB: Used for real-time data like delivery partner tracking, \ncaching frequent queries, and storing unstructured data \nsuch as session information.\n  Example: A NoSQL database stores the real-time location \nof delivery partners, allowing the app to show current partner \npositions on a map.\n\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Real Time Tracking DB: Used for real-time data like delivery partner tracking, \ncaching frequent queries, and storing unstructured data \nsuch as session information.\n  Example: A NoSQL database stores the real-time location \nof delivery partners, allowing the app to show current partner \npositions on a map.\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 231,
      "versionNonce": 996104215,
      "index": "bA9",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "JscHcuHEoxFjo3yalNOHE",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 6627.814224700385,
      "y": 17010.924631914473,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "width": 1537.8448054731225,
      "height": 432.67543059819513,
      "seed": 1835984281,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1727671131867,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 49.44862063979371,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "- SQL databases ensure ACID transactions, ensuring that\n  critical processes like order creation and payment processing \n  are consistent and reliable.\n   * Refer DB table details for db table schema.\n\n- Implements sharding for horizontal scaling\n- Uses read replicas to improve read performance",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- SQL databases ensure ACID transactions, ensuring that\n  critical processes like order creation and payment processing \n  are consistent and reliable.\n   * Refer DB table details for db table schema.\n\n- Implements sharding for horizontal scaling\n- Uses read replicas to improve read performance",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 286,
      "versionNonce": 2052548631,
      "index": "bAA",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "5WaapjeCtEzTjwaOA_3fn",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 2626.440950768678,
      "y": 20859.570755377645,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "width": 1934.1559750933407,
      "height": 977.1741038864047,
      "seed": 456394105,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1727672190807,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 48.85870519432022,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Processing and Sending Alerts: Real-Time Components\n* Real-Time Tracking:  Delivery partners’ locations are tracked using \n    GPS data, and the data is pushed to a NoSQL database for quick access.\n\n* Notification Layer:  Push Notifications are sent via services like \nFirebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) to inform customers and delivery \npartners of updates (e.g., “Your order is on the way”).\n\n* SMS or In-App Alerts: SMS for delivery partners or customers, \nand in-app alerts for real-time updates.\n\n\nCaching Layer\nRedis/Memcached: Frequently accessed data like popular restaurant lists, \nfrequently ordered items, or active delivery partners are cached to reduce \nload on databases and improve response time.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Processing and Sending Alerts: Real-Time Components\n* Real-Time Tracking:  Delivery partners’ locations are tracked using \n    GPS data, and the data is pushed to a NoSQL database for quick access.\n\n* Notification Layer:  Push Notifications are sent via services like \nFirebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) to inform customers and delivery \npartners of updates (e.g., “Your order is on the way”).\n\n* SMS or In-App Alerts: SMS for delivery partners or customers, \nand in-app alerts for real-time updates.\n\n\nCaching Layer\nRedis/Memcached: Frequently accessed data like popular restaurant lists, \nfrequently ordered items, or active delivery partners are cached to reduce \nload on databases and improve response time.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
