    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 408,
      "versionNonce": 2085092265,
      "index": "bAZ",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "4xP52rLHn4QkFpPxQgvyA",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": -32.805248368687444,
      "y": 25599.787209546885,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "width": 2078.234608299579,
      "height": 1154.924475606544,
      "seed": 515354311,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1728525735079,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 54.34938708736678,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "** Functional Requirements **\n- Users can subscribe to X no of stocks and set rules based on stock prices.\n\n- Rule Types:\n    Users can define rules based on stock metrics such as:\n     - Opening Price: Notify if it goes above/below a threshold.\n     -  Current Price: Notify if it crosses a certain value or changes by a %.\n     - Moving Average: Notify if stock price deviates from the moving average.\n\n- Real-Time Stock Data Processing: \n     Continuously scan stock price changes from an external service/API.\n\n- Rule Evaluation: \n     Check more than 1 million user-defined rules against stock price changes.\n\n- Notify user if any rule is satisfied. Notifications must be sent within a \nminute.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "** Functional Requirements **\n- Users can subscribe to X no of stocks and set rules based on stock prices.\n\n- Rule Types:\n    Users can define rules based on stock metrics such as:\n     - Opening Price: Notify if it goes above/below a threshold.\n     -  Current Price: Notify if it crosses a certain value or changes by a %.\n     - Moving Average: Notify if stock price deviates from the moving average.\n\n- Real-Time Stock Data Processing: \n     Continuously scan stock price changes from an external service/API.\n\n- Rule Evaluation: \n     Check more than 1 million user-defined rules against stock price changes.\n\n- Notify user if any rule is satisfied. Notifications must be sent within a minute.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 268,
      "versionNonce": 1540031559,
