      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1728525765374,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 51.188269045870406,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "** API Endpoints **\n\nUser Management:\n - POST /users/register: Register a new user.\n - POST /users/login: Authenticate the user.\n\nStock Subscription:\n - Subscribe to stock price changes.\n     POST /users/{userId}/stocks/subscribe\n     Payload: { \n                  \"stockSymbol\": \"ABC\", \n                  \"rules\": [{ \n                               \"type\": \"price\", \n                               \"operator\": \">\", \n                               \"value\": 100 \n                              }] \n                }\n\n - Un-Subscribe to stock price changes.\n     POST /users/{userId}/stocks/unsubscribe\n\n - Get list of subscribed stocks.\n    GET /users/{userId}/stocks\n\nRule Management:\n - POST /users/{userId}/rules: Create a rule for a stock.\n - GET /users/{userId}/rules: List all rules set by the user.\n - DELETE /users/{userId}/rules/{ruleId}: Delete a specific rule.\n\nNotification Management:\n - GET /users/{userId}/notifications: Retrieve user notifications.\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "** API Endpoints **\n\nUser Management:\n - POST /users/register: Register a new user.\n - POST /users/login: Authenticate the user.\n\nStock Subscription:\n - Subscribe to stock price changes.\n     POST /users/{userId}/stocks/subscribe\n     Payload: { \n                  \"stockSymbol\": \"ABC\", \n                  \"rules\": [{ \n                               \"type\": \"price\", \n                               \"operator\": \">\", \n                               \"value\": 100 \n                              }] \n                }\n\n - Un-Subscribe to stock price changes.\n     POST /users/{userId}/stocks/unsubscribe\n\n - Get list of subscribed stocks.\n    GET /users/{userId}/stocks\n\nRule Management:\n - POST /users/{userId}/rules: Create a rule for a stock.\n - GET /users/{userId}/rules: List all rules set by the user.\n - DELETE /users/{userId}/rules/{ruleId}: Delete a specific rule.\n\nNotification Management:\n - GET /users/{userId}/notifications: Retrieve user notifications.\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 144,
      "versionNonce": 472743303,
      "index": "bAm",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "Zsr-msYqUmY6PN4in4lYT",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 76.10376184610368,
      "y": 32067.59126187588,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "width": 1522.490062713623,
      "height": 1110.5539772727248,
      "seed": 1725541833,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
