      "fontSize": 32.04314226418547,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "- Read msg from SQS\n- Parse messages\n- finds alerts that need \n  to be triggered in batches\n- sends out payload to \n  communication module \n  to trigger email, push \n  notifications\n- marks the alerts as \n  triggered in the database \n- deletes messages from SQS\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Read msg from SQS\n- Parse messages\n- finds alerts that need \n  to be triggered in batches\n- sends out payload to \n  communication module \n  to trigger email, push \n  notifications\n- marks the alerts as \n  triggered in the database \n- deletes messages from SQS\n",
