      "fontSize": 34.43809071691436,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "- Here, AWS step function can be used \nto fetch stock prices from exchange, \nthen publish the msg to SQS\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
