rized data     |\n                                   +---------+-----------+\n                                              |\n                                              v\n                                   +---------------------+\n                                   | External Consumers  |\n                                   | (Cities, Researchers)|\n                                   | Access summarized   |\n                                   | data by hour        |\n                                   +---------------------+\n",
