      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Monitoring & Alerting\n\n- Tracks system health \n- send alerts on failures/anomalies.\n- Retrieves data from job storage \n  & job queue to monitor job \n  execution times, failures, and retries.\n- Integrate with monitoring tools like \nPrometheus and Grafana for visual dashboards.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Monitoring & Alerting\n\n- Tracks system health \n- send alerts on failures/anomalies.\n- Retrieves data from job storage \n  & job queue to monitor job \n  execution times, failures, and retries.\n- Integrate with monitoring tools like \nPrometheus and Grafana for visual dashboards.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
