      "updated": 1754711944849,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 26.488406206500695,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "- SQS supports Automatic Retry \n- When msg fails, it is re-attempted \n  based on the queue’s visibility timeout.\n- SQS supports integrated DLQs. \n- When msg has exceeded its retry limit, \n  it automatically moves to the DLQ, \n   with no additional configuration needed.\n- Scalability: SQS is fully managed, \n   highly scalable, and requires minimal \n   configuration. \n- It's easier to setup & maintain compare \n  to RabbitMQ.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- SQS supports Automatic Retry \n- When msg fails, it is re-attempted \n  based on the queue’s visibility timeout.\n- SQS supports integrated DLQs. \n- When msg has exceeded its retry limit, \n  it automatically moves to the DLQ, \n   with no additional configuration needed.\n- Scalability: SQS is fully managed, \n   highly scalable, and requires minimal \n   configuration. \n- It's easier to setup & maintain compare \n  to RabbitMQ.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
