      "updated": 1756081149229,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Stream Processors\n(Flink/Spark/KStreams)  \n- Consume from Kafka\n- Aggregate in sliding windows (1m, 5m)\n- Emit pre-aggregated metrics\n- Downsample for long-term storage\n- Write raw to hot storage (e.g. VictoriaMetrics) \n- Write aggregates to both hot & cold storage \n ",
      "fontSize": 34.227946064807625,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Stream Processors\n(Flink/Spark/KStreams)  \n- Consume from Kafka\n- Aggregate in sliding windows (1m, 5m)\n- Emit pre-aggregated metrics\n- Downsample for long-term storage\n- Write raw to hot storage (e.g. VictoriaMetrics) \n- Write aggregates to both hot & cold storage \n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
