      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Interview script\n“I’ll lean on OpenSearch for the inverted index. It’s the \nright lever for postings and AND queries, leaving us to \nfocus on correctness, visibility, and cost. Kafka + Flink \nkeeps the pipeline exactly-once; Postgres/Redis hold \noperational metadata.”",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Interview script\n“I’ll lean on OpenSearch for the inverted index. It’s the \nright lever for postings and AND queries, leaving us to \nfocus on correctness, visibility, and cost. Kafka + Flink \nkeeps the pipeline exactly-once; Postgres/Redis hold \noperational metadata.”",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
