      "text": "Gateway emits telemetry locally:\n- The Gateway sends metrics/logs/traces to \n   localhost where the sidecar is listening.\n- This is extremely fast (in-memory or very low latency)\n\nGateway immediately continues:\n- The Gateway doesn't wait for acknowledgment \n  from the remote monitoring system.\n- It trusts the sidecar to handle the delivery.\n\nSidecar handles the heavy lifting:\n- Buffering, batching, retry logic\n- Network communication to the monitoring backend\n- Compression, authentication, etc.\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 27.169696881804494,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gateway emits telemetry locally:\n- The Gateway sends metrics/logs/traces to \n   localhost where the sidecar is listening.\n- This is extremely fast (in-memory or very low latency)\n\nGateway immediately continues:\n- The Gateway doesn't wait for acknowledgment \n  from the remote monitoring system.\n- It trusts the sidecar to handle the delivery.\n\nSidecar handles the heavy lifting:\n- Buffering, batching, retry logic\n- Network communication to the monitoring backend\n- Compression, authentication, etc.\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
